ed="T" n="0720c14"/><persName key="A001896">釋懷迪</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000031270">循州</placeName>人也。先入法于<placeName key="PL000000031280">南樓寺</placeName>，其山半<lb
ed="T" n="0720c15"/>在海涯，半連陸岸，乃仙聖遊居之靈府也。<lb
ed="T" n="0720c16"/><persName key="A001896">迪</persName>久探經論，多所該通，《七略》、<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g377"/>九流<ptr type="glossary" target="#g378"/>，粗加尋<lb
ed="T" n="0720c17"/>究。以海隅之地，津濟之前，數有<name>梵</name>僧寓止<lb
ed="T" n="0720c18"/>于此，<persName key="A001896">迪</persName>學其書語，自茲通利。<persName key="A001358">菩提流志</persName>初<lb
ed="T" n="0720c19"/>譯《寶積》<ptr target="#n96"/>，召<persName key="A001896">迪</persName>至<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>，事畢南歸。後於<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣<lb
ed="T" n="0720c20"/>府</placeName>遇一<ref type="person" target="#A000992"><name>梵</name>僧</ref>，齎多羅葉經一夾，請共飜傳，<lb
ed="T" n="0720c21"/>勒成十卷，名《大佛頂萬行首楞嚴經》<ptr target="#n379"/>是也。<lb
ed="T" n="0720c22"/><persName key="A001896">迪</persName>筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>經旨，緝綴文理，後因<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g380"/>南使附經入<lb
ed="T" n="0720c23"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，即<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>中</date>也。又<date from-iso="+0758-03-22" key="j19979941998315" to-iso="+0759-02-06"><name>乾元</name>元年</date>有<placeName key="PL000000055418">罽賓</placeName>三藏<persName key="A000994">般<lb
ed="T" n="0720c24"/>若力</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000048208">中天竺</placeName>婆羅門<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g117"/>三藏<persName key="A009133">善部末摩</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000055417">箇失密</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0720c25"/>三藏<persName key="A009135">舍那</persName>並慕化入朝，詔以<persName key="A000994">力</persName>為太常少<lb
ed="T" n="0720c26"/>卿，<persName key="A009133">末摩</persName>為鴻臚少卿，並員外<ptr type="glossary" target="#g381"/>置，放還本土。<lb
ed="T" n="0720c27"/>或云：「各齎經至，屬<placeName key="PL000000000514">燕</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000001058">趙</placeName>阻兵<ptr target="#n382"/>，不遑宣譯，故<lb
ed="T" n="0720c28"/>以官品榮之。」</p>
